Bright Content
--------------

Bright Content is Python Weblog software built from reusable components

Copyright 2006 Uche Ogbuji and Julian Krause.
Licensed under the Academic Free License version 3.0

http://brightcontent.net

Bright Content requires requires Python 2.4 or more recent.  Install it using
easy_install as follows:

easy_install brightcontent

If this does not work you are probably not set up for easy_install.
Follow the simple instructions at

http://peak.telecommunity.com/DevCenter/EasyInstall

easy_install will automatically take care of installing dependencies for
you.

